title: After wireless charging, the phone does not turn on
content:
Hi everybody!
I bought a powerbank with wireless charging function (interstep 10DQi). I put the phone on charge. After 30 minutes, I took it off and it turned off. Now you can't turn it on. Only if you put it back on the charger. It doesn't charge from the wire.
I record video with problem: youtu.be /6eKAO1z-D_I
I need help. What should I do now?
